Hey <%= @recipient_name %>,

<p>Hope this email finds you well. My name is Haider Ali and I'm the founder of <a href="https://tablr.io" target="_blank">Tablr</a> - we help businesses like <%= @company_name %> turn customer reviews into actionable insights.</p>

<p>Here's the thing - most restaurants collect hundreds of reviews but never get actionable insights from them. We built Tablr to change that.</p>

<p>We have analyzed <%= @reviews_count %> latest reviews for <%= @company_name %> and found key analytics that you might not have noticed:</p>

<ul>
  <li><%= @positive_reviews_count %> positive, <%= @negative_reviews_count %> negative and <%= @neutral_reviews_count %> neutral reviews</li>
  <li>Guests love <%= @positive_keywords.first(2).map { |keyword| keyword[:name].to_s.titleize }.reject(&:blank?).to_sentence(two_words_connector: ' and ', last_word_connector: ', and ') %> the most</li>
  <li>While some comlains about <%= @complaint_topics.first(2).map { |topic| topic[:text].to_s.titleize }.reject(&:blank?).to_sentence(two_words_connector: ' and ', last_word_connector: ', and ') %></li>
  <%if @suggestion_topics.present?%>
    <li>Suggestions coming from customers are
     <ul>
      <% @suggestion_topics.first(2).each do |topic| %>
      <li><%= topic[:text].to_s.titleize %></li>
     <% end %>
     </ul>
    </li>
  <%end%>
</ul>

<p>We have already helped restaurants increase their revenue by an average of 22% by identifying these hidden profit killers. Please visit <%= link_to 'Full Report',  Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.report_path(@place.place_actor_run_id), { target: '_blank' } %> to view complete analysis of customer reviews.</p>

